{"tid":1540612,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[升級] 今晚十點！全城怒哮！五大訴求！缺一不可！追究黑警！釋放義士！","createTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:55:03.000Z","uid":127929,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"caed0a3ee379adc87c89d4a3d4e51817d83fea27","tid":1540612,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">林鄭你同黑警黑社會成班殺人犯害死咁多人，毀人一生，諗住撤回就算玩鳩我地？</span><br />\n<br />\n太遲喇，而家已經唔係6月既不撤不散喇仆街！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />袋住先？我袋你老母呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次直接跟下面大嗌！全世界落街又好係屋企都好，<span style=\"color: red;\">同我一字不漏嗌足半個鐘！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五大訴求！缺一不可！<br />\n解散警隊！釋放義士！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"8a277f46405070d79aeb8cfe060ed37c3477d159","tid":1540612,"uid":311358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"點解宣布「暫緩」既時候唔洗經立法會動議，而家撤回就要？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1539874\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1539874</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cd42c85a73d8a0ce6c76ed0600120d99d8a01bcf","tid":1540612,"uid":317299,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcJFfrO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcJFfrO.jpg&h=7f9dd8d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TjeJddu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTjeJddu.jpg&h=e690fd03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sHcuNJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsHcuNJL.jpg&h=417a49e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不反對通知書申請中<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src